Package com.telekom.m2m.cot.restsdk Description

Cloud of Things Java SDK

For further information see Readme.md or https://github.com/cloud-of-things/cot-java-rest-sdk

To access the cloud of things server you instantiate a CloudOfThingsPlatform with the necessary CotCredentials. Then you can get all the individual *Api classes for the different parts from the CloudOfThingsPlatform.

Since:
0.2.0
